DESCRIPTION:Hi Mike-\n\nSending along a calendar invite to get the demo 
 officially on the calendar. As we get closer to the date\, we can pivot 
 if needed.\n\nBelow and attached\, please find additional information.  
 If you have any questions\, please feel free to reach out!\n\nBUILDING A
 CCESS:\nAttached\, please find an Agency site map with garage access ins
 tructions. If driving\, visitor parking is located directly following th
 e entrance and spots are marked as visitor spots. Building security will
  give you access to our floor (6th floor) and our receptionist will be a
 ble to direct you into the meeting room.\n\nTECH SET-UP:\nI’ve scheduled
  15-minutes right before the scheduled demo time for a tech set-up with 
 our tech manager. The hope is to get you connected to the meeting room T
 V + audio.\n\nCATERING:\nPlease see catering recommendations below. Addr
 ess to provide for Catering/ Lunch vendor: 409 N Houston St Dallas TX 75
 202\, STE 600 (Building name: The Luminary). Our receptionist will direc
 t catering on where to set up. Our creative/ production team consists of
  around 20 folks\, but I can confirm this number as we get closer to the
  demo date.\n\nMEETING SCHEDULE:\nI’ve allocated 1hr for the demo presen
 tation (12pm - 1pm)\, let me know if you have any concerns with this!\n\
 n\n  *   Mendocino Farms<https://www.mendocinofarms.com/catering/>\n  * 
   East Hampton Sandwich Co<https://www.ehsandwich.com/catering-1/>\n  * 
   Velvet Taco<https://www.velvettaco.com/catering/>\n  *\nCommissary<htt
 ps://www.commissarydallas.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/comm.135_Cateri
 ngMenu_Digital3.pdf>\n  *\nHawaiian Bros<https://catering.hawaiianbros.c
 om/HB0022/Dallas-TX-Greenville>\n  *   Chiloso<https://chilosomexicanbis
 tro.com/catering/> Mexican Bistro<https://chilosomexicanbistro.com/cater
 ing/> <https://chilosomexicanbistro.com/catering/>\n\n\nLERMA/ Agency\n4
 09 N Houston ST STE 600\nDallas\, TX 75202\n(214) 891-4100\n\n\n\nDAYANA
  GURROLA\n\nBusiness Affairs\n\nCell 214.620.1630\n[LERMA/]<https://lerm
 aagency.com/>\n[signature_3959691437]\n\n\n
