DESCRIPTION:Join Zoom Meeting\n\nhttps://us02web.zoom.us/j/81010715589?p
 wd=jkOsGwxw3IxPdIdlXM1J5VaFMwm5NO.1\n\nFrom the folks who brought you St
 udio Awesome\, Select Casting (formerly SelectVO) has been the trusted v
 oiceover casting platform for the majority of U.S. ad agencies since 201
 9. Our streamlined workflow saves producers hours of busywork — and beca
 use every project runs through top talent agencies\, clients only receiv
 e curated auditions from real\, working actors. No pay-to-play noise. Ev
 er.\n\nThis year\, we’ve expanded in a few key ways beyond VO that are a
 lready making a big impact for our ad clients:\n\nOn-Camera Casting: Bui
 lt for internal/lower-budget shoots where there's no budget for a castin
 g director. Everything (headshots\, self-tapes\, notes) stays organized 
 in one place — no more Dropbox chaos.\n\nAudio Services (via Studio Awes
 ome): Emmy-winning\, bilingual engineers for VO record and mix. Flexible
  with budget\, and clients save ~30% on average.
